for any and all classes level 50 and above.<br>
<br>
The Ancients are a small guild of mature players(25  ).  Are main goals are having fun,<br>
leveling up, and killing what we can.  We are not a &quot;uber&quot; guild.<br>
<br>
Our playing goals are to gain enough members to do the following:<br>
1. Begin fighting in PoP zones and begin to work our way through them.<br>
2. Get everyone in the guild there Epic, if they desire it.<br>
3. Be able to fight in some of the higher end zones to get everyone in the guild well equipped.<br>
<br>
However, the goals mentioned above will never be done at the expense of having fun!!<br>
<br>
We are a small guild and very much like a family.  We are not willing to change that, just to <br>
become a &quot;high end&quot; guild.  If this sounds like a good fit for you, please come check us out.<br>
<br>
We are a part of a larger gaming club called &quot;The Old Geezers&quot;.  Please feel free to poke around<br>
our website at www.ogzr.org for more info.<br>
<br>
We do have several requirements that need to be meet before becoming an Ancient.<br>
1. 25 years old and/or act like it on a consistent basis <br>
2. Able to play 2 to 3 nights a week.  Also, most of now are in the Eastern time zone.<br>
Playing time is usually 9:00 pm to 11:00 pm most nights, give or take a little.<br>
3. Do what you say, and say what you can do <br>
4. No whining <br>
<br>
Feel free to contact any of the following in game:<br>
<br>
Stumpmen - Guild Leader<br>
Retepga - Officer<br>
Vaos - Officer<br>
<br>
The process for becoming an Ancient will be a 1 to 2 week feeling out process between the guild<br>
and yourself.  This is just to make sure we are &quot;right&quot; for each other.  After that, you will<br>
be invited into the guild, and then be in a 2 week probation period.<br>
<br>
